sertor-flow — governance/SDLC bundle
=====================================

This package vendors development-method assets from GitHub Spec Kit, pinned at
version 0.8.18:

  - .claude/skills/speckit-*/ and .claude/skills/speckit-git-*/ (SpecKit skills)
  - .claude/agents/speckit-*.md (SpecKit agents)
  - .specify/templates/** (spec/plan/tasks/checklist/constitution templates)
  - .specify/scripts/{bash,powershell}/** (scaffolding scripts)
  - .specify/extensions/git/** (git extension)
  - .specify/workflows/** (workflow registry)

